WEBVTT

01:42.360 --> 01:47.200
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

02:10.919 --> 02:11.800
Careful!

02:16.800 --> 02:17.720
Changyu.

02:18.560 --> 02:19.800
I can explain.

02:19.880 --> 02:20.840
You lied to me.

02:20.920 --> 02:22.880
You lied to me in Lin'an.

02:22.960 --> 02:24.120
You lied to me in the camp.

02:24.200 --> 02:25.840
You have been lying all along.

02:25.920 --> 02:27.720
Was that injury fake too?

02:29.880 --> 02:31.240
Are you hurt?

02:31.800 --> 02:32.720
Do not touch me.

02:34.880 --> 02:36.200
What you just said,

02:36.280 --> 02:37.480
I can explain all of it.

02:39.040 --> 02:40.320
You need treatment. Let's go back.

02:42.160 --> 02:43.560
I am just a butcher's daughter.

02:44.240 --> 02:46.280
How could I trouble
the exalted Marquis Wu'an?

02:49.720 --> 02:50.960
I am not allowed to care?

02:52.360 --> 02:53.880
Then why drug me and run to war?

02:54.560 --> 02:56.000
Do you know what a battlefield is?

02:56.080 --> 02:58.280
It is where lives
are worth less than dirt!

02:59.400 --> 03:00.480
Did you forget what I told you

03:00.560 --> 03:02.320
after the sheep and salt incident?

03:02.400 --> 03:04.320
So you were deceiving me back then too,

03:04.400 --> 03:06.200
weren't you?

03:07.640 --> 03:09.920
Marquis Wu'an, is it fun deceiving people?

03:11.120 --> 03:12.520
I went to war

03:12.600 --> 03:14.360
because you deceived me.

03:14.920 --> 03:15.880
I drugged you

03:15.960 --> 03:18.360
because I was afraid you would die there.

03:27.800 --> 03:28.920
I can die.

03:29.000 --> 03:30.800
But you must live well.

03:40.160 --> 03:41.440
If I fall,

03:42.960 --> 03:44.200
take Fan Changning

03:45.000 --> 03:46.280
and settle somewhere quiet.

03:48.400 --> 03:49.640
Open a braised meat shop.

03:50.160 --> 03:51.880
Raise pigs if you like.

03:51.960 --> 03:53.240
As long as you live,

03:53.880 --> 03:55.320
you may live however you wish.

04:01.240 --> 04:03.200
Find yourself a gentle scholar,

04:03.280 --> 04:04.560
have children.

04:05.480 --> 04:06.640
I will not interfere.

04:55.520 --> 04:57.440
But as long as I live,

04:58.360 --> 04:59.360
in this lifetime,

05:00.320 --> 05:01.400
you are mine.

05:27.240 --> 05:30.000
Madam, your man Man Di is gravely injured.

05:30.760 --> 05:32.560
-Where is he?
-Jin Yuanbao took him back to camp.

05:32.640 --> 05:34.400
Madam, your headscarf.

05:39.200 --> 05:40.320
Marquis.

05:40.400 --> 05:41.600
The strategist is injured!

05:42.280 --> 05:44.480
Wake up.

05:45.080 --> 05:47.720
You have been with us
since you were barely ten.

05:47.800 --> 05:49.840
If you leave without a word,

05:49.920 --> 05:52.280
how am I supposed
to answer to your sister?

05:57.160 --> 05:58.240
What happened to Man Di?

05:59.480 --> 06:01.280
He was stabbed clean through the chest.

06:01.360 --> 06:02.440
Blood would not stop.

06:03.320 --> 06:04.680
The lady physician came earlier.

06:05.520 --> 06:07.360
She shook her head
and left without a word.

06:09.320 --> 06:10.480
How could this happen?

06:11.160 --> 06:14.240
When we were clearing the field,

06:14.840 --> 06:18.720
a young soldier suddenly leapt up

06:18.800 --> 06:20.400
from a pile of corpses.

06:31.760 --> 06:32.760
-Man Di!
-Man Di!

06:40.760 --> 06:41.680
Was he

06:41.760 --> 06:43.800
the boy guarding the catapult?

06:44.320 --> 06:45.560
Yes, that one.

06:50.680 --> 06:52.000
I should not have hesitated.

06:54.240 --> 06:56.240
If I had killed him then,

06:57.440 --> 06:59.280
Man Di would not be lying here now.

07:04.080 --> 07:05.680
We told you not to crowd around.

07:06.360 --> 07:07.400
What is going on?

07:07.480 --> 07:09.320
Lady Doctor, please save him.

07:10.040 --> 07:11.200
He is fine. It is not fatal.

07:12.440 --> 07:13.480
Not fatal?

07:13.560 --> 07:16.000
You told me he was stabbed
through the chest.

07:17.320 --> 07:19.320
The blade pierced his breastplate.

07:21.360 --> 07:22.520
Thankfully, it blocked the blow.

07:22.600 --> 07:23.880
No organs were harmed.

07:25.600 --> 07:26.520
That breastplate…

07:27.800 --> 07:29.880
Man Di's sister asked me
to give it to him.

07:31.760 --> 07:32.760
All you grown men

07:32.840 --> 07:34.920
covered your eyes
when I cleaned the wound,

07:35.000 --> 07:36.880
too squeamish to look.

07:37.560 --> 07:39.680
Now you are frightening yourselves.

07:39.760 --> 07:40.640
Look at his face.

07:40.720 --> 07:43.560
His… lips. Even a corpse
would not look that pale.

07:43.640 --> 07:44.560
He was frightened badly.

07:45.640 --> 07:46.800
His body is weak to begin with.

07:48.040 --> 07:49.600
That is why I told you not to crowd him.

07:49.680 --> 07:50.800
Let him rest properly.

07:50.880 --> 07:52.440
Man Di is fine.

07:52.520 --> 07:53.640
I have others to tend to.

07:53.720 --> 07:54.560
Thank you.

07:56.600 --> 07:57.440
That is a relief.

07:58.440 --> 07:59.600
He is fine, Yuanbao.

07:59.680 --> 08:00.560
As long as he is fine.

08:00.640 --> 08:01.640
As long as he is fine.

08:15.880 --> 08:16.880
Pull it out.

08:25.680 --> 08:28.000
Report! General Shi Hu was slain
by an enemy woman soldier

08:28.080 --> 08:29.680
with a butcher's knife.

08:32.480 --> 08:33.400
What did you say?

08:33.480 --> 08:34.880
Shi Hu was slain by a woman soldier.

08:34.960 --> 08:36.400
My brother…

08:39.640 --> 08:40.840
Impossible.

08:41.360 --> 08:43.400
My brother could fight off 10,000 men.

08:43.480 --> 08:46.960
General Shi Hu could fight off 10,000 men!

08:47.040 --> 08:48.240
I saw it with my own eyes.

08:48.320 --> 08:49.920
He was disarmed of his golden hammer.

08:50.000 --> 08:51.480
Three blows. No.

08:51.560 --> 08:52.880
Two blows and he was finished.

08:55.760 --> 08:57.160
I said that is impossible.

08:58.320 --> 08:59.800
-Go verify it again!
-Yes.

09:00.840 --> 09:01.840
No.

09:04.480 --> 09:07.160
That must have been Fan Changyu.

09:10.600 --> 09:11.720
Fan Changyu…

09:12.880 --> 09:14.440
Report! The Yanzhou and Jizhou armies

09:14.520 --> 09:15.920
are advancing from the southwest.

09:16.000 --> 09:16.880
They're closing in.

09:17.480 --> 09:19.360
Our army is now attacked on three sides.

09:20.960 --> 09:21.840
Prepare to depart.

09:23.720 --> 09:25.680
My father awaits us in Lucheng.

09:25.760 --> 09:27.240
Your Highness…

09:27.760 --> 09:29.400
I said retreat.

09:36.960 --> 09:38.520
Your Highness is right.

09:39.200 --> 09:40.600
Prince Changxin's great cause

09:42.040 --> 09:43.040
cannot be delayed.

09:44.720 --> 09:45.600
Retreat!

09:48.840 --> 09:51.360
I fought with everything I had
trying to stop him.

09:51.440 --> 09:52.560
Still, I failed.

09:53.280 --> 09:54.600
Shi Yue took Sui Yuanqing.

09:55.200 --> 09:56.520
And I ended up wounded.

09:58.760 --> 10:01.160
A scholar truly has no place
on the battlefield.

10:01.240 --> 10:03.000
I told you to wear armor,
and you would not.

10:03.080 --> 10:04.680
Had to copy Kongming instead.

10:04.760 --> 10:05.800
Not even close.

10:08.520 --> 10:09.720
Xie Jiu.

10:09.800 --> 10:11.760
Go to the Yanzhou camp
and fetch Doctor Lu.

10:12.320 --> 10:13.920
-Yes.
-Wait.

10:18.160 --> 10:19.880
This little scratch of mine

10:19.960 --> 10:21.560
hardly calls for a military physician.

10:21.640 --> 10:23.760
No need for a cannon to kill a fly.

10:25.400 --> 10:26.720
So the injury is not serious?

10:27.400 --> 10:28.320
Fine.

10:28.400 --> 10:29.560
Go fetch the veterinarian.

10:29.640 --> 10:31.480
-Yes.
-Wait.

10:32.920 --> 10:36.360
There is not another physician
anywhere in this camp?

10:39.480 --> 10:40.560
Then perhaps

10:40.640 --> 10:42.160
I should invite the Grand Princess

10:42.240 --> 10:43.080
to examine you.

10:46.240 --> 10:47.920
Go tell Her Highness

10:48.000 --> 10:49.520
my injuries are grave.

10:49.600 --> 10:51.200
My life hangs by a thread.

10:51.280 --> 10:54.120
But you do not look that bad.

10:54.200 --> 10:56.480
Of course, you cannot see it
from the outside.

10:57.080 --> 10:58.480
Inside, I am already rotten.

11:00.400 --> 11:01.520
Understood.

11:03.320 --> 11:05.200
I have matters to attend to.
I'll head out.

11:27.000 --> 11:29.920
I hear your wounds
are beyond saving, Mr. Gongsun.

11:30.000 --> 11:32.560
So I came to chant a few sutras
for your passing.

11:32.640 --> 11:34.360
Om mani padme hum.

11:34.440 --> 11:35.360
Om mani padme hum.

11:37.920 --> 11:39.720
Om mani padme hum.

11:39.800 --> 11:42.440
-Om mani padme hum.
-Stop that.

11:43.360 --> 11:45.320
Another chant and you will
really send me off.

11:54.560 --> 11:56.440
Mr. Gongsun,

11:56.520 --> 11:58.640
you must have endured
much hardship along the way.

11:59.280 --> 12:00.240
None at all.

12:01.120 --> 12:02.680
The Marquis bears the burden of the realm.

12:02.760 --> 12:03.880
I admire him deeply.

12:04.600 --> 12:06.520
Following him through hardship
is my own choice.

12:06.600 --> 12:07.720
Nothing bitter about it.

12:09.000 --> 12:11.800
In the clash with the Chongzhou army,

12:11.880 --> 12:13.880
the Marquis escaped danger in the end.

12:14.400 --> 12:16.320
There is no need to worry about him.

12:16.400 --> 12:19.680
I am not worried
about that rascal of a disciple.

12:20.200 --> 12:21.440
Half a month ago,

12:21.520 --> 12:24.440
among the Jizhou soldiers
delivering grain up the mountain

12:24.520 --> 12:26.520
was half a disciple of mine.

12:27.120 --> 12:29.800
She went up with the convoy
and never came back down.

12:29.880 --> 12:32.440
I have no idea what has become of her.

12:32.520 --> 12:34.760
A grain courier?

12:34.840 --> 12:35.680
Yes.

12:35.760 --> 12:37.080
And your disciple?

12:37.160 --> 12:38.080
Yes.

12:38.160 --> 12:39.400
But from what I know,

12:39.480 --> 12:41.800
you are extremely selective
about disciples.

12:42.960 --> 12:44.480
Across the whole of Dayin,

12:44.560 --> 12:47.000
only Xie Zheng ever met your standards.

12:47.080 --> 12:48.840
So how did some random soldier on the road

12:48.920 --> 12:50.080
earn your favor?

12:50.160 --> 12:51.360
And only half of it at that?

12:52.240 --> 12:54.120
That girl has exceptional bones.

12:54.200 --> 12:57.800
A rare prodigy for martial arts.

12:58.640 --> 13:02.080
Only her wit falls a bit short.
She hates reading.

13:02.160 --> 13:05.280
So I count her

13:05.360 --> 13:06.200
as half a disciple.

13:08.160 --> 13:09.120
A girl…

13:09.960 --> 13:11.400
Your Highness, slow down!

13:12.040 --> 13:12.880
Careful!

13:14.760 --> 13:16.840
Your Highness, are you all right?

13:22.640 --> 13:24.560
Your Highness, this is hardly proper.

13:24.640 --> 13:26.120
Xie Jiu said he was dying.

13:26.200 --> 13:27.880
-What propriety matters now?
-Wait for me!

13:28.600 --> 13:29.640
Grand Tutor,

13:30.560 --> 13:33.640
the disciple you mentioned,
is her surname Fan?

13:35.040 --> 13:36.920
Indeed it is. Fan Changyu.

13:37.000 --> 13:38.480
Nineteen years old.

13:39.000 --> 13:40.960
Why do you ask? Do you know her?

13:42.320 --> 13:44.560
-So my troublesome disciple knows her too?
-Gongsun!

13:52.440 --> 13:54.480
This is the man Xie Jiu said
was at death's door?

13:56.320 --> 13:58.400
Almost there.
Already rotting on the inside.

14:00.400 --> 14:03.040
Your Highness the Grand Princess.
My respects.

14:03.120 --> 14:03.960
Your Highness!

14:05.120 --> 14:07.440
If you will excuse me. Your Highness!

14:07.960 --> 14:10.360
Your Highness, please let me explain.
Your Highness!

14:10.440 --> 14:11.960
Careful, Your Highness.

14:12.040 --> 14:12.920
Please hear me out.

14:13.000 --> 14:14.080
Your Highness, please.

14:14.160 --> 14:15.680
Why would you toy with me like this?

14:15.760 --> 14:17.800
I was not toying with you. I…

14:17.880 --> 14:19.040
Forgive me.

14:20.640 --> 14:21.560
I…

14:22.640 --> 14:24.160
I simply did not expect

14:24.880 --> 14:26.960
Your Highness to rush here
in such concern for me.

14:27.520 --> 14:28.440
So I…

14:35.600 --> 14:36.440
Don't take them off.

14:37.480 --> 14:38.560
Too late.

14:42.640 --> 14:43.720
It was my fault.

14:44.320 --> 14:45.720
I only remembered

14:45.800 --> 14:48.000
how Your Highness encouraged me
before the campaign.

14:48.080 --> 14:48.840
Headmaster.

14:49.840 --> 14:51.280
What I said this morning

14:51.360 --> 14:53.400
was merely to encourage the soldiers.

14:53.480 --> 14:54.360
Don't read too much into it.

14:57.880 --> 15:00.240
You seem perfectly well.

15:00.320 --> 15:02.280
There are other wounded soldiers
who need my care.

15:03.200 --> 15:04.560
I will take my leave.

15:08.040 --> 15:10.720
-Your Highness, does it hurt?
-Yes. But I can bear it.

15:24.440 --> 15:25.280
Mrs. Fan.

15:25.800 --> 15:27.680
The kitchen made ginger broth.

15:27.760 --> 15:28.880
I brought you a bowl.

15:29.720 --> 15:31.480
No need, General Xie Jiu.

15:31.560 --> 15:32.480
Give it to someone else.

15:47.360 --> 15:48.320
Is there anything else?

16:08.000 --> 16:09.160
When I hid the truth from you,

16:09.840 --> 16:11.080
it was not by choice.

16:11.160 --> 16:12.760
I had been framed.

16:13.440 --> 16:14.440
I was hunted down

16:15.440 --> 16:16.720
and ended up stranded in Lin'an.

16:18.280 --> 16:20.360
By chance, you saved me from the snow.

16:20.440 --> 16:22.440
If I had told you who I was then,

16:23.240 --> 16:24.680
it might have brought danger upon you.

16:25.200 --> 16:26.960
So I chose to keep it hidden.

16:28.600 --> 16:30.600
I never blamed you
for hiding it back then.

16:32.880 --> 16:34.800
Then you resent me
for hiding it this time?

16:46.560 --> 16:47.760
When you came looking for me,

16:47.840 --> 16:49.080
I was truly happy.

16:49.880 --> 16:50.800
But I also knew

16:51.440 --> 16:52.960
that once you learned the truth,

16:53.040 --> 16:53.960
you'd be more frustrated.

16:55.280 --> 16:57.120
So all those explanations

16:57.800 --> 16:59.680
never made it past my lips.

17:07.480 --> 17:08.640
Ning was taken

17:09.760 --> 17:11.160
because of my identity.

17:11.920 --> 17:13.319
For that, I owe you an apology.

17:14.880 --> 17:16.160
I do not blame you

17:17.359 --> 17:18.200
for Ning being taken.

17:19.280 --> 17:21.040
You were wounded trying to save her.

17:21.640 --> 17:23.280
When you deceived me on the mountain…

17:26.119 --> 17:27.359
I do not blame you for that either.

17:39.680 --> 17:41.240
You blame me for nothing.

17:41.320 --> 17:43.000
So what you are saying is that we should

17:43.080 --> 17:44.240
simply part ways?

17:47.360 --> 17:48.760
We were never truly together.

17:52.240 --> 17:53.280
What parting is there to speak of?

17:55.840 --> 17:56.840
What did you just say?

17:58.840 --> 18:00.880
What do you mean we were never together?

18:00.960 --> 18:01.960
What are you trying to say?

18:18.440 --> 18:19.920
We had an agreement.

18:22.240 --> 18:23.520
You would marry into my family
in name only.

18:24.560 --> 18:27.440
But there was never
anyone called Yan Zheng.

18:28.440 --> 18:30.320
If Yan Zheng never existed,

18:32.520 --> 18:33.800
then that marriage contract

18:33.880 --> 18:35.120
never existed either.

18:37.480 --> 18:38.920
Then why did you come looking for me?

18:39.920 --> 18:41.520
Why promise to support me
by working as a butcher?

18:41.600 --> 18:43.680
Why take it upon yourself
to go to war in my place?

18:43.760 --> 18:45.280
I came looking for Yan Zheng.

18:49.480 --> 18:51.600
-Not Xie Zheng.
-What difference does that make?

18:52.280 --> 18:53.960
-They are both me.
-It is different.

18:58.280 --> 18:59.640
I cannot see you…

19:01.960 --> 19:03.920
see Marquis Wu'an as Yan Zheng.

19:05.520 --> 19:07.160
Marquis Wu'an is a hero of the realm.

19:07.960 --> 19:08.960
Born to a great house.

19:09.560 --> 19:11.520
If he were with a butcher girl,

19:12.680 --> 19:14.200
the whole world would laugh.

19:24.600 --> 19:26.480
I know my place well enough.

19:28.800 --> 19:30.440
Whom I marry is my decision.

19:31.040 --> 19:32.200
What concern is it of the world?

19:32.880 --> 19:34.480
You are not merely a butcher girl.

19:34.560 --> 19:36.200
You are a heroine of great merit.

19:36.280 --> 19:38.320
If you truly fear the world's ridicule,

19:38.880 --> 19:39.920
then fine.

19:40.760 --> 19:42.120
I'll ask His Majesty
to grant our marriage.

19:43.200 --> 19:44.320
We can be together openly.

19:44.920 --> 19:46.080
Who would dare mock us then?

20:07.800 --> 20:08.760
Changyu.

20:10.240 --> 20:11.480
My name is Xie Zheng.

20:12.400 --> 20:13.560
Courtesy name Jiuheng.

20:15.360 --> 20:16.840
Born to a military family.

20:17.360 --> 20:18.560
A man from the capital.

20:18.640 --> 20:19.960
Enfeoffed as Marquis Wu'an.

20:22.800 --> 20:23.960
With a sincere heart,

20:25.480 --> 20:26.640
I ask for your hand in marriage.

20:29.080 --> 20:30.720
May we live in peace

20:31.360 --> 20:33.080
and grow old together.

21:22.720 --> 21:23.680
I see.

21:48.120 --> 21:49.200
Teacher.

21:53.440 --> 21:54.440
What brings you here?

21:54.520 --> 21:57.400
That injury of yours is rather peculiar.

21:57.920 --> 22:00.360
It does not look like something
you got in battle.

22:00.880 --> 22:02.240
More like one from a brawl.

22:02.320 --> 22:04.600
Do not tell me you were beaten by…

22:07.760 --> 22:09.480
In this battle, Prince Changxin lost

22:09.560 --> 22:11.280
one of his fiercest generals, Shi Hu.

22:11.840 --> 22:13.080
Yet Shi Yue managed a surprise strike

22:13.160 --> 22:14.480
and rescued Sui Yuanqing.

22:15.600 --> 22:16.960
That was a failure in my planning.

22:17.800 --> 22:20.920
The Shi brothers were Prince Changxin's

22:21.000 --> 22:22.840
two strongest commanders.

22:22.920 --> 22:24.120
Now that Shi Hu is dead,

22:24.200 --> 22:26.240
he has effectively lost an arm.

22:28.360 --> 22:31.880
I heard that by the time you arrived
to receive the Yanzhou reinforcements,

22:31.960 --> 22:33.640
Shi Hu was already dead.

22:33.720 --> 22:36.800
Who in your army
could possibly defeat such a man?

22:40.160 --> 22:42.040
His wife killed him.

22:42.640 --> 22:44.320
Wife? Whose wife?

22:45.080 --> 22:47.320
His wife? You are married?

22:47.400 --> 22:49.640
Did you not swear you would never marry?

22:50.720 --> 22:53.120
And yet you never even told me?

22:53.840 --> 22:55.200
It is a long story.

22:55.960 --> 22:58.280
Let's call it a marriage born of hardship.

22:58.360 --> 22:59.880
Hardship?

23:01.160 --> 23:02.200
I will not ask you.

23:02.800 --> 23:04.720
You tell me.
How did that woman kill Shi Hu?

23:05.320 --> 23:06.960
At the time, we were badly outnumbered.

23:07.040 --> 23:08.640
The Marchioness snatched
Shi Hu's war hammer

23:08.720 --> 23:10.440
-and struck him three times, ending his--
-What?

23:11.320 --> 23:14.160
Three blows killed Shi Hu?

23:14.240 --> 23:16.320
Then she must come
from a line of famous generals.

23:17.880 --> 23:19.800
-No.
-No?

23:20.400 --> 23:22.840
Then she must be an extraordinary woman.

23:22.920 --> 23:24.200
Jiuheng,

23:24.280 --> 23:26.560
you must treat her well.

23:28.120 --> 23:29.120
Shi Hu is dead.

23:29.200 --> 23:31.960
Shi Yue will not let this pass.

23:32.040 --> 23:33.960
And Prince Changxin

23:34.480 --> 23:36.120
has his sights firmly set on Lucheng.

23:36.200 --> 23:38.920
How do you plan to deal with this?

23:41.320 --> 23:42.920
If I commit the Xie army

23:43.000 --> 23:45.640
and join forces with He Jingyuan
to crush Prince Changxin,

23:45.720 --> 23:47.440
someone else will be waiting
to reap the spoils.

23:48.840 --> 23:50.200
Right now,

23:50.280 --> 23:51.920
Wei Yan is trying to cover up

23:52.000 --> 23:54.040
Wei Xuan's grave mistake in the northwest.

23:54.120 --> 23:55.640
The best move for him

23:56.400 --> 23:58.640
is to seize the credit
for crushing the Chongzhou rebels.

24:02.200 --> 24:03.560
In my view,

24:03.640 --> 24:05.840
letting him take that credit
may not be a bad thing.

24:09.360 --> 24:10.760
Why do you say that, Grand Tutor?

24:10.840 --> 24:12.960
Tell me. Who else in Dayin

24:13.040 --> 24:15.240
was granted a marquisate
before turning 20?

24:15.920 --> 24:18.360
The higher you climb, the harder you fall.

24:18.440 --> 24:21.480
Even if you defeat the rebels
and return to the capital

24:21.560 --> 24:22.640
with great merit,

24:23.240 --> 24:25.920
what more could His Majesty
possibly reward you with?

24:26.720 --> 24:29.720
The court is treacherous these days.

24:29.800 --> 24:31.720
Better to temper your brilliance

24:31.800 --> 24:36.440
and watch others
fight each other to the death.

24:37.080 --> 24:38.640
You mean,

24:38.720 --> 24:41.000
let the Li clan and Wei Yan
fight it out first,

24:41.080 --> 24:42.520
while we wait to reap the benefit?

24:45.960 --> 24:47.760
Wei Yan holds the military command.

24:47.840 --> 24:50.920
He Jingyuan guards Jizhou for him.

24:51.000 --> 24:52.840
For years,

24:52.920 --> 24:57.600
Li Xing has not dared
confront Wei Yan directly.

24:57.680 --> 25:02.320
Otherwise, he would never have sent
his beloved eldest grandson, Li Huai'an,

25:02.400 --> 25:04.880
to the northwest to serve in the army.

25:05.880 --> 25:07.360
Then, by that reasoning,

25:07.440 --> 25:08.960
Prince Changxin's rebellion

25:09.040 --> 25:11.320
could be a scheme for the Li clan
on the military power?

25:11.400 --> 25:15.760
The Li clan may scheme,
but not to that extent.

25:15.840 --> 25:20.040
However, Prince Changxin's
eldest son, Sui Yuanhuai,

25:20.640 --> 25:24.200
has long been rumored
to have secret dealings with the Li clan.

25:24.800 --> 25:25.760
No smoke without fire.

25:25.840 --> 25:27.560
It is very suspicious.

25:27.640 --> 25:29.560
Sui Yuanhuai…

25:30.080 --> 25:32.800
That reminds me of something.

25:33.840 --> 25:37.920
After Crown Prince Chengde
and Xie Linshan fell in battle at Jinzhou,

25:38.000 --> 25:40.000
the late emperor suddenly abdicated

25:40.080 --> 25:43.200
and passed the throne
to the current emperor, Qi Sheng.

25:44.280 --> 25:46.280
Soon after, a great fire
broke out in the Eastern Palace.

25:46.360 --> 25:49.280
The crown princess and her son
perished in the flames.

25:51.520 --> 25:55.800
At the time, Princess Changxin was
at the Eastern Palace with her eldest son.

25:55.880 --> 25:58.680
The boy was burned so badly,
his face could no longer be shown.

25:59.520 --> 26:01.720
Yet the late emperor
offered no compensation.

26:02.320 --> 26:04.440
Prince Changxin has kept
a low profile for years.

26:04.520 --> 26:05.640
His resentment toward the court

26:05.720 --> 26:07.800
is beyond doubt.

26:09.200 --> 26:10.200
Once down the mountain,

26:10.880 --> 26:12.160
send word to the capital.

26:12.240 --> 26:14.280
Investigate the Eastern Palace fire
in secret.

26:16.000 --> 26:18.000
Prince Changxin's eldest son,
Sui Yuanhuai,

26:18.080 --> 26:19.360
has a trusted aide named Zhao Xun.

26:19.960 --> 26:22.520
A seal from the Eastern Palace
is in his possession.

26:24.080 --> 26:25.160
Sixteen years ago,

26:25.240 --> 26:27.400
when the Eastern Palace burned,

26:28.040 --> 26:29.640
I was among the few who survived.

26:30.560 --> 26:31.640
Yet now,

26:31.720 --> 26:34.320
Sui Yuanhuai has issued
an order to capture him.

26:34.400 --> 26:36.240
We must find Zhao Xun

26:36.320 --> 26:37.280
before he does.

26:50.560 --> 26:53.360
Just now, in Mr. Gongsun's tent,

26:53.440 --> 26:55.720
it was not appropriate for me
to pry into your personal affairs.

26:56.640 --> 26:57.840
But now I will ask you plainly.

26:57.920 --> 26:59.480
This marriage of yours,

26:59.560 --> 27:01.800
did you take a proper wife
or merely a concubine?

27:02.920 --> 27:04.680
A proper wife, of course.

27:04.760 --> 27:06.160
If it is a legitimate marriage,

27:06.240 --> 27:09.040
why do you look so glum?

27:15.560 --> 27:17.000
I hid my identity from her.

27:18.000 --> 27:19.040
Now that she knows

27:19.560 --> 27:21.720
she would be marrying Marquis Wu'an,

27:21.800 --> 27:22.960
she refuses.

27:24.000 --> 27:25.280
She says

27:25.360 --> 27:27.600
she never needed military merit
to stand beside me.

27:29.360 --> 27:31.920
A clear-minded woman.

27:33.760 --> 27:36.560
Very much like the young disciple

27:36.640 --> 27:38.160
I recently took in at Baxia.

27:40.400 --> 27:42.480
Even if you offered to trade
her husband for Marquis Wu'an,

27:42.560 --> 27:43.920
she would still refuse.

27:45.200 --> 27:46.520
My wife is much the same.

27:46.600 --> 27:49.840
Titles and riches mean nothing to her.

27:49.920 --> 27:51.720
They are not worth
as much as a bowl of rice.

27:53.600 --> 27:56.240
Give her a few roast chickens

27:56.320 --> 27:58.360
and she would be happier than an immortal.

27:58.440 --> 28:00.680
She works without ever complaining,

28:00.760 --> 28:03.120
with strength that never seems to run out.

28:03.720 --> 28:08.000
Laughing and smiling all day long.

28:09.680 --> 28:11.000
Why do I feel

28:11.080 --> 28:12.640
they are talking about the same person?

28:16.480 --> 28:17.840
Sir.

28:17.920 --> 28:20.000
I have a request.

28:20.600 --> 28:21.840
Speak.

28:21.920 --> 28:23.560
I ask that you accept my wife

28:23.640 --> 28:25.080
as your adopted daughter.

28:26.680 --> 28:30.480
So you wish to give her
a respectable family to stand behind her,

28:30.560 --> 28:32.000
to silence the gossip of others.

28:33.280 --> 28:34.280
Yes.

28:35.040 --> 28:36.880
I do not care about her origins.

28:37.400 --> 28:38.560
But I will not allow people

28:38.640 --> 28:40.760
to use them to slander her.

28:43.600 --> 28:45.000
And what if the girl refuses?

28:45.080 --> 28:47.080
What if she only wishes
to live as an ordinary commoner?

28:50.000 --> 28:51.360
I will respect her choice.

28:52.720 --> 28:55.320
But if she chooses to stay with me,

28:55.920 --> 28:57.480
I will never let her suffer again.

28:58.240 --> 28:59.400
I did not expect

29:00.360 --> 29:02.280
such devotion from you.

29:02.360 --> 29:03.960
Just like your mother.

29:07.200 --> 29:08.160
Very well.

29:09.000 --> 29:11.560
I agree.

29:15.160 --> 29:18.520
Your new wife, what is her name?

29:18.600 --> 29:20.040
How old is she?

29:20.120 --> 29:21.880
Her surname is Fan. Her name is Changyu.

29:21.960 --> 29:23.080
She is 19.

29:25.160 --> 29:27.200
Your… Your wife?

29:28.200 --> 29:29.080
Your female disciple?

29:29.160 --> 29:30.480
You married into her family?

29:30.560 --> 29:32.320
You were taken to repair the dam?

29:35.320 --> 29:36.160
You…

30:15.680 --> 30:16.720
Marquis--

30:19.880 --> 30:21.040
What is it?

30:21.120 --> 30:22.600
It's already near midnight.

30:22.680 --> 30:23.600
You should rest.

30:25.560 --> 30:26.760
How is Xie Wu's injury?

30:26.840 --> 30:28.400
The physician says
his organs are unharmed.

30:28.480 --> 30:29.560
He only needs rest.

30:30.680 --> 30:31.640
Good.

30:33.320 --> 30:34.480
Bring me my horse.

30:35.000 --> 30:36.120
-Marquis… This…
-Do it.

30:37.680 --> 30:38.720
Yes.

31:17.160 --> 31:19.600
‎XIE

31:26.320 --> 31:28.200
The Marquis ordered you
to stand guard here?

31:28.720 --> 31:29.840
Yes.

31:31.320 --> 31:32.560
I will not leave the camp.

31:33.280 --> 31:35.520
Please help keep an eye on Ning for me.

31:36.840 --> 31:37.720
Of course.

32:34.880 --> 32:36.600
Who is there? Come out!

32:41.200 --> 32:42.320
It is me.

32:46.360 --> 32:47.240
What are you doing here?

32:48.880 --> 32:49.720
Could not sleep.

32:50.600 --> 32:52.000
Came out to clear my head.

32:53.640 --> 32:54.880
You cannot sleep either?

32:56.920 --> 32:59.160
I saw too many bodies on the battlefield.

33:00.720 --> 33:01.960
It is weighing on my chest.

33:10.880 --> 33:12.520
The first time I went to war,

33:15.120 --> 33:16.280
I could not sleep either.

33:17.440 --> 33:18.960
I had nightmares all night.

33:20.680 --> 33:22.160
The second time I went to battle,

33:22.240 --> 33:24.000
I killed even more men than the first.

33:26.520 --> 33:27.520
That whole night,

33:28.480 --> 33:29.720
I could not sleep at all.

33:31.840 --> 33:34.400
So I went to the river
and started fishing.

33:35.400 --> 33:36.560
Fished the entire night.

33:37.160 --> 33:38.560
Until I was completely worn out.

33:40.120 --> 33:41.480
That night, I fell asleep right away.

33:43.680 --> 33:44.920
After that,

33:45.640 --> 33:47.120
the nightmares stopped.

33:53.320 --> 33:54.600
It is all behind you now.

34:09.080 --> 34:10.560
If you are still feeling restless,

34:11.080 --> 34:11.960
we can spar a little.

34:15.920 --> 34:17.560
What is it? Afraid?

34:21.920 --> 34:22.800
Come on.

34:46.360 --> 34:48.440
What was that?
Repaying kindness with a blow?

34:48.520 --> 34:49.719
In war, deception is fair play.

34:51.120 --> 34:52.400
That is a convincing argument.

34:53.520 --> 34:55.239
You were not fighting seriously.

34:55.320 --> 34:57.360
On the battlefield,
I would never beat you.

34:57.440 --> 34:59.800
Close combat favors speed.

35:00.320 --> 35:01.360
You wield short blades well,

35:01.440 --> 35:02.640
but rely too much on brute force.

35:03.320 --> 35:05.040
Use less force. Follow the momentum.

35:05.120 --> 35:06.440
Use more finesse.

35:06.520 --> 35:07.480
Increase your speed.

35:09.760 --> 35:10.880
-Again.
-Come.

35:32.720 --> 35:34.200
Just now, you were holding back.

35:34.800 --> 35:36.280
I am not a fool.

35:36.360 --> 35:38.320
I had to test your moves first.

35:39.560 --> 35:40.400
Again.

35:46.160 --> 35:47.880
This one is ready. Careful, it is hot.

35:59.840 --> 36:02.080
This is delicious. Sweet and sour.

36:02.160 --> 36:03.480
Did you bring seasoning?

36:04.680 --> 36:05.920
No.

36:06.000 --> 36:06.920
I picked some wild berries.

36:07.600 --> 36:09.400
Some are sour, some a little spicy.

36:10.800 --> 36:11.960
So you tasted them all first?

36:24.320 --> 36:25.920
Why? Does it taste bad?

36:34.760 --> 36:36.080
Do not treat me so well.

36:37.520 --> 36:38.600
You are Marquis Wu'an.

36:40.360 --> 36:42.080
I am just a butcher woman.

36:43.160 --> 36:44.760
You are the best woman
I could ever ask for.

36:45.720 --> 36:47.200
I like you.

36:49.280 --> 36:50.360
Well, don't.

36:53.000 --> 36:55.240
You should marry someone
of equal standing.

36:56.480 --> 36:57.680
Live a glorious life,

36:58.520 --> 37:00.000
admired by thousands.

37:05.360 --> 37:06.760
Admired by thousands…

37:08.720 --> 37:10.320
Everything I have today

37:10.400 --> 37:11.800
I earned with military merit.

37:11.880 --> 37:13.320
Not admiration.

37:15.480 --> 37:16.920
If I, Marquis Wu'an,

37:17.000 --> 37:18.040
have to worry

37:18.560 --> 37:20.600
about what the world thinks
of my marriage,

37:20.680 --> 37:22.120
that would be truly pitiful.

37:25.800 --> 37:26.880
Before this,

37:27.920 --> 37:29.840
I never even considered marriage.

37:31.440 --> 37:32.800
My uncle lives without affection.

37:33.320 --> 37:34.880
My mother loved too deeply.

37:35.400 --> 37:36.760
Neither life was what I wanted.

37:37.840 --> 37:40.120
I was born on the battlefield
and expected to die there.

37:40.720 --> 37:42.080
I believed

37:43.160 --> 37:44.960
I was destined to fall in battle.

37:46.440 --> 37:47.360
So,

37:48.520 --> 37:51.080
I never wanted a woman
to spend her life mourning me.

37:53.560 --> 37:54.800
But after meeting you,

37:55.720 --> 37:56.960
I suddenly found

37:58.920 --> 38:00.200
I am a little afraid to die.

38:14.240 --> 38:15.120
Enough about me.

38:15.640 --> 38:16.600
Tell me about you.

38:17.280 --> 38:19.120
After we're through with this war,

38:19.200 --> 38:20.120
what do you want to do?

38:21.280 --> 38:24.800
Raise and slaughter pigs?

38:28.000 --> 38:29.280
The future is too far away.

38:30.600 --> 38:32.440
I can only think
about what is in front of me.

38:33.560 --> 38:35.040
I promised Ning

38:35.120 --> 38:36.520
I would find Qian and Bao'er.

38:37.680 --> 38:39.000
And Mr. Zhao.

38:39.080 --> 38:40.440
And Jin Yuanbao and his men.

38:41.600 --> 38:43.840
And all the townfolks
scattered in foreign lands.

38:45.240 --> 38:46.880
I want to bring them home.

38:48.080 --> 38:49.720
Lin'an may have been destroyed,

38:51.040 --> 38:52.720
but we can rebuild it

38:53.960 --> 38:56.440
with our own hands, brick by brick.

38:58.760 --> 38:59.640
Good.

39:00.320 --> 39:02.320
When all this is over,

39:02.960 --> 39:04.400
I'll request a post in the northwest.

39:05.280 --> 39:06.120
Then,

39:06.200 --> 39:08.480
everything in the capital
will have nothing to do with me.

39:09.520 --> 39:12.040
When the time comes,
I will rebuild Lin'an with you.

39:12.120 --> 39:13.240
What do you think?

39:16.800 --> 39:17.920
You would really…

39:19.920 --> 39:20.800
stay in Lin'an?

39:24.320 --> 39:26.400
The days I spent in Lin'an with you

39:27.120 --> 39:28.680
were the happiest days

39:28.760 --> 39:30.000
of my life.

39:32.160 --> 39:34.600
Zheng! Mrs. Zhao says come eat lunch!

39:34.680 --> 39:37.800
Every morning, I woke up to the sound
of you slaughtering pigs.

39:39.880 --> 39:42.760
Then Ning, Mr. Zhao, and I

39:42.840 --> 39:43.680
would play chess.

39:43.760 --> 39:44.960
Build snowmen together.

39:47.120 --> 39:47.960
At noon,

39:48.040 --> 39:50.320
I could eat your pork intestine noodles.

39:51.520 --> 39:54.760
And listen to Mrs. Zhao
gossip about the village.

39:54.840 --> 39:56.200
Thirty taels!

39:58.600 --> 39:59.840
Look who is here!

40:00.680 --> 40:02.520
At night, we would sit together,

40:04.120 --> 40:06.720
studying calligraphy together
to the sound of crickets.

40:08.360 --> 40:09.600
All of it.

40:12.320 --> 40:13.720
I miss every bit of it.

40:33.440 --> 40:35.000
You hold my hand so tight.

40:35.520 --> 40:37.760
Aren't you afraid you'll make
your hand bleed again?

40:39.600 --> 40:41.040
I am more afraid you will hit me.

40:41.120 --> 40:43.360
That is because you keep kissing me
out of nowhere.

40:44.400 --> 40:45.240
Fists down,

40:45.320 --> 40:46.800
and I won't kiss you out of nowhere.

40:51.000 --> 40:51.960
Try it.

43:29.920 --> 43:33.080
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

43:33.160 --> 43:34.000
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
